'''Knave Leader''' was the leader of [[Knave Squadron]] during the [[Battle of Calamari]]. He flew an [[E-7 E-wing multi-role starfighter|E-wing]] during the battle and ordered his squadron to blast anything that looked like a scanning tower on the [[World Devastator]]s.

